texts.text: Patch 41 was a version of Wii U Edition released on November 14, 2018.[1] [edit]

MCCE-8189 – Grass block sides have the wrong color.
Fixed a crash that can occur for client players when a sticky piston moves a slime block attached to another sticky piston.
Fixed Auto Jump not allowing players to stay underwater.
Fixed the players' head rotation while in minecarts.
Fix for guardians not spawning around ocean monuments.
